{
  "stem": "10587.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had guards standing outside that were not quite visible to make sure that the Germans, because we would have to disperse because they would have probably arrested a lot of people, and-- and they would have beaten a lot of people as well.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know if they would have killed anybody at that time, but they would definitely do a lot of harm.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't remember exactly how we got there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think we-- we must have gone by train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were, at that time, they did not call-- I think-- that at that time, it was not-- I know that the city became Judenrein at that time, when we left Auschwitz or Oswiecim.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I think they called it more like a resettlement to the city of Sosnowiec.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- and life totally changed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were cramped in a one, two room place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] like a-- we were just shoved in in two rooms, which were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] limited-- with limited bathrooms and wash-- and a place where you can wash up.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was-- life changed completely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a few weeks later, a few months later, they started to take my older brother, my older sisters to-- to forced labor camps.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and they worked in a-- they worked in a-- in a factory sewing uniforms.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were also guarded by women guards at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At the start, I understand, and we were able to write and get letters and-- and my-- I remember, when my parents would write to my sisters, tell them to be strong and to work hard and to be clean and neat, and-- because the [INAUDIBLE], you know, which is to the aunt, the-- the-- an aunt-- [INAUDIBLE] means freedom is-- is close.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then life totally changed, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was not the same.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a time of sadness, because you-- they were taking the kids away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they took--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Left?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was left with my-- and my younger brother, [INAUDIBLE] and I-- Joshua-- and I and my mother and father were left.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were resettled in Sosnowiec, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it-- I don't think they resettled in the same building even.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Food was rationed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and food was a big problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you could not go into certain places, because they said Juden forboden.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that means you cannot enter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So in the beginning, I would take my star off, and-- and we spoke German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We spoke Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I would be able to buy a loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it-- food became a problem at the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Also, the curfew was even much stricter than in Oswiecim.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the Poles were also very rough on the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they-- because they had their stores were open.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they would-- they would-- they would point out if you-- if they knew that you-- and-- and then you were sent to prison for doing-- for violating the-- to go into place where it said Juden forboden.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the-- it was a big building that we were in Sosnowiec.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The-- I remember when we came to Sosnowiec, we were-- we came to a high school that was the place where they assigned different locations for you, where you [? assigned, ?] what I would call, some rooms that you can live in.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were there for a few days in this-- it was very, very hot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember, I got very sick, because I was-- like I had like a sunstroke from that-- from being exposed to the sun and not having enough food.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and everything was a problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Even water-- to get some water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So from this place, we were reassigned to locations in the Jewish part of Sosnowiec.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Sosnowiec, there's a very large Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was a much bigger city, than Oswiecim.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 12 SECONDS] And from Sosnowiec, then they took us to Srodula, to the ghetto, which was right outside the city of Sosnowiec.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- I think we might-- we walked there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We walked-- you have to leave everything, whatever you could carry, come clothes you were able to take.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, whatever they could, they took.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was-- it-- and that helped to get to buy, you know, things on the black market.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Bread and-- and-- whatever food we could-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we could get at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it-- it was a rough time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The star-- right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that-- yeah, no, they-- no, I would not because my parents were very concerned about the children, and they kept us pretty much in-- sheltered",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Srodula.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
